SELECT p.portfolio_name, p.total_value, COUNT(fp.property_id) AS num_properties FROM portfolio p JOIN financial_performance fp ON p.portfolio_id = fp.portfolio_id GROUP BY p.portfolio_name, p.total_value HAVING COUNT(fp.property_id) > 3 ORDER BY num_properties DESC;

SELECT f.date, f.income, f.expenses, f.net_profit, p.portfolio_name FROM financial_performance f JOIN portfolio p ON f.portfolio_id = p.portfolio_id WHERE f.date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY f.date ASC LIMIT 10;
